  <?dbhtml filename="xauth.html"?>

  <title>xauth-&xauth-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      xauth is a small utility to read and manipulate Xauthority files, which
      are used by servers and clients alike to control authentication and
      access to X sessions.
    </para>

